This is Perl module lib::xi.

INSTALLATION

Install cpanm (App::cpanminus) and then run the following command to install
lib::xi:

    $ cpanm lib::xi

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf lib-xi-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd lib-xi-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

lib::xi documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc lib::xi

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

